Create Customer Report Use Case Description:

Use Case: Create Customer Report extends Create Reports

Context: The actor intends to create the Customer Report

Actors: Manager, ChocAn Data Center

Main Success Scenario:
	3e.1. The Create Customer Report option is selected.
	3e.2. The following data is generated: A list of all services provided to the customer for that week, sorted by the date of service. It also 
		includes Member Name, Member Number, Member Street Address, Member City, Member State, Member Zip Code, and for each service provided it includes date
		of service, provider name, and service name.
	3e.3. The report is saved as a file to the disk.	  

Extensions:
	N/A